<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Liko Lango Moja Wazi TZR121</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Liko lango moja wazi,
 Ni lango la mbinguni;
 Na wote waingiao
 Watapata nafasi.

[V2]
 Lango ndiye Yesu Bwana
 Wote waingie kwake,
 Lango! Lango
 La Mbinguni li wazi.

[V3]
 Yesu ndiye lango hili,
 Hata sasa li wazi,
 Kwa wakubwa na wadogo,
 Tajiri na maskini.

[V4]
 Hili ni lango la raha,
 Ni lango la rehema;
 Kila mtu apitaye
 Hana majonzi tena.

[V5]
 Tukipita lango hili
 Tutatua mizigo,
 Tuliochukua kwanza,
 Tutavikwa uzima.

[V6]
 Hima ndugu tuingie
 Lango halijafungwa,
 Likifungwa mara moja
 Halitafunguliwa.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>121</hymn_number>
</song>